item.title: CVE-2017-6148|2024-09-17T00:06:49.247Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28ltm%2C%20aam%2C%20afm%2C%20apm%2C%20asm%2C%20link%20controller%2C%20pem%2C%20websafe%29
item.description: Responses to SOCKS proxy requests made through F5 BIG-IP version 13.0.0, 12.0.0-12.1.3.1, 11.6.1-11.6.2, or 11.5.1-11.5.5 may cause a disruption of services provided by TMM. The data plane is impacted and exposed only when a SOCKS proxy profile is attached to a Virtual Server. The control plane is not impacted by this vulnerability.
